headline: US Kids Food and Beverage Market Forecast and Company Analysis Report 2025-2033 Conagra, PepsiCo, Kellogg, Campbell Soup, General Mills, Nestle, Lifeway Foods, The Hershey Company
summary: The United States Kids Food and Beverage Market is projected to surge to US$ 100.16 billion by 2033 from US$ 57.02 billion in 2024, marking a CAGR of 6.46% from 2025 to 2033. This growth is driven by increased health consciousness, demand for organic products, and innovative offerings addressing parental concerns over childhood obesity and influenced by social media marketing. headline: General Mills (GIS): A Food Dividend Stock Worth Watching
summary: General Mills, Inc. (NYSE:GIS) is included among the 10 Best Food Stocks with Dividends. The company’s top priority for fiscal 2026 is to revive organic sales growth driven by volume. To achieve this, it plans to increase investments in consumer value, product innovation, brand building, and new offerings— all guided by its established experience framework. […]
